sys_hub_action_type_definition.description:
This action retrieves Group ID for the given Group Name from Workplace by Facebook.

Inputs:

  • Group Name - The Group Name to fetch Group ID from Workplace by Facebook. E.g. ECSD.

Outputs:

  • Status - Will be set to "Success" if the request succeeds or "Error" if a failure occurs.
  • Error Message - Will be populated when the status is "Error".
  • Group ID - ID of the group retrieved from given group name. Will be populated in case of success.

Error Messages:

  • OAuth access token is not valid.
  • Group Name does not exist.

To use this action, the corresponding Workplace by Facebook connection and credential must be created and associated with the Workplace by Facebook Connection & Credential alias. Learn More

Additional Note:

  • There can be multiple groups with the same name in Workplace by Facebook, this action retrieves the group id of the first match from response.

Note: Requires a subscription for production use. Read More.
